Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Chinese visit rattles USSR
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bx2y
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 11 Feb 1979
Chinese deputy premier's visit to US threatens detente with USSR. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.